    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure><img data-src="/3A0005/Users\Asus\workblog\source_posts\3A0001\SimplySpeak-cover.png" alt="Simply-Speak"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">Simply-Speak</figcaption></figure><h1 id="simply-speak-极简朗读-day0005">Simply Speak 极简朗读 |DAY0005</h1><p>同学们好，欢迎来到 Simply Speak 极简朗读课。</p><p>今天朗读的内容，是一则新闻，讲述如何协助遇到诈骗的亲友。</p><p><span id="more"></span></p><p>请同学在屏幕展示下一页幻灯片时，点击暂停播放，自己按照幻灯上的文字内容朗读一遍，然后再继续播放课程内容。这是一个大大提升你的学习效率的秘密技巧。</p><figure><img data-src="/3A0005/Users\Asus\workblog\source_posts\3A0005\3A0005.001.png" alt="3A0005.001"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">3A0005.001</figcaption></figure><p>现在，我们为文字标注了汉语拼音，请同学再次暂停播放，自行朗读一遍，你这次的朗读目标，是要把刚才不会念的字词读对，确保发音正确。</p><figure><img data-src="/3A0005/Users\Asus\workblog\source_posts\3A0005\3A0005.002.png" alt="3A0005.002"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">3A0005.002</figcaption></figure><p>现在，请同学按照老师为文本标注的笔记，把文字上方有着重号的字词给重读。重读的意思是，发音比其他字词大声一些、读得慢一些、声调高一些。此外，你可以在有斜线号的地方换气，或是在需要时短暂地停下来。具体做法，请参考老师的示范。</p><figure><img data-src="/3A0005/Users\Asus\workblog\source_posts\3A0005\3A0005.003.png" alt="3A0005.003"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">3A0005.003</figcaption></figure><p>好了，今天的课就讲到这里，恭喜你又学完一堂课啦！快到作业区提交作业吧！我们下节课再见！</p><p><a href="https://classroom.google.com/c/NzE1NjI2NzY5NzUy/a/NzI5NTU5MDI1NTk1/details"><span style="background-color:#00aa90"><font color="#FFFFFF">提交作业 (code:fxiuaaf) </font></span></a></p><p><a href="https://classroom.google.com/c/NzE1NjI2NzY5NzUy/a/NzI5NTU5MDI1NTk1/details"><span style="background-color:#00aa90"><font color="#FFFFFF">Please submityour assignments on Google Classroom (code: fxiuaaf)</font></span></a></p><div class="video-container"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fi_giuXaXtc" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" allowfullscreen></iframe></div>]]></content>
    
    
